oracle.olapi.metadata.mapping

Class AttributeMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • oracle.olapi.metadata.BaseMetadataObject
      • oracle.olapi.metadata.PublicMetadataObject
        • oracle.olapi.metadata.mapping.ObjectMap
          • oracle.olapi.metadata.mapping.ValueMap
            • oracle.olapi.metadata.mapping.AttributeMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MetadataObject

    public final class AttributeMap
extends ValueMap
    A ValueMap that maps an MdmAttribute for an MdmDimension to an Expression. An application creates an AttributeMap with the findOrCreateAttributeMap method of a DimensionMap. An application that supports multiple languages must provide a separate AttributeMap for each language.
